1
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,480
Chu Muzhi,

2
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:15,360
I found what you wanted.

3
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,640
Let's meet.

4
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:18,360
Sure.

5
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:19,640
I'll send you the address.

6
00:00:29,460 --> 00:00:33,740
=Half-awake=

7
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:37,420
=Episode 23=

8
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,040
Chu Muzhi.

9
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,040
I'm here.

10
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,120
Where's my stuff?

11
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,480
Where's Qianyu?

12
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:22,640
Didn't expect

13
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,240
you figured it out so fast.

14
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:26,760
Tell me where she is now.

15
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,880
Or I'll destroy the ring.

16
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,520
You'll never get it then.

17
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,700
If you don't give it to me,

18
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,200
how will I know you're not lying?

19
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,800
(It's my dad's ring.)

20
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,080
(He really has it.)

21
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,080
You've got the ring.

22
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,640
Just tell me where Qianyu is.

23
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,480
I'm sorry.

24
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,520
I can't return

25
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,560
Xiao Qianyu to you.

26
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,600
She's dead.

27
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,840
You ended her life?

28
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,720
Yeah.

29
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,480
I did it.

30
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,560
No.

31
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,120
But don't you want to know

32
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,880
how she died?

33
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:46,180
(Cautionary Note: It's purely fictional.
Do not attempt to imitate.)

34
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,480
You're a monster.

35
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,520
What exactly did she do

36
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,800
to make you end her life?

37
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,240
She saw something she shouldn't have.

38
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,440
It was bad luck for her.

39
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,640
She saw

40
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,920
me take Wang Yaqin's life.

41
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,340
Don't move.

42
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:11,100
(Cautionary Note: It's purely fictional.
Do not attempt to imitate.)

43
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,760
Chu Muzhi,

44
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,440
you can't get away.

45
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,440
I know exactly who you are.

46
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,600
You're the son of that loan shark.

47
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,680
If Gu Yixiao knows it,

48
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,880
he won't let you off.

49
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,120
Do you think,

50
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,760
with you here,

51
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,960
who stands a better chance?

52
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,520
Gu Yixiao,

53
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,000
if you don't show up soon,

54
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:37,640
your wife will be fed to the dog.

55
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,640
Where are you?

56
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,920
At the place you first saved me.

57
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,640
Remember it?

58
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,120
Take a guess

59
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,000
how long till Gu Yixiao gets here.

60
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,520
Chu Muzhi,

61
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:33,840
you think you've got everything
under control.

62
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,800
Back then,

63
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:47,680
you got close to Gu Yixiao
on purpose, didn't you?

64
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,160
Your dad went missing.

65
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,680
You suspected Gu Yixiao killed him,

66
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,720
so you approached him,

67
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,200
and pretended to be his friend.

68
00:06:02,020 --> 00:06:03,760
Later, my dad found out
who you really were.

69
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,390
And then you had someone
cause his death.

70
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,360
So my dad's death wasn't an accident.

71
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,160
But there's something I don't get.

72
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,920
Why didn't you take revenge
all these years?

73
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,240
Instead, you helped him so much.

74
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,560
Do you not resent him at all?

75
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,360
You've crossed my line.

76
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,200
You can leave now.

77
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,080
I

78
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,040
am waiting for an answer.

79
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,840
Xingwan!

80
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,960
Ye Xingwan!

81
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,600
Let her go.

82
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,680
The answer is about to come out.

83
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,080
One more step and I'll end her life.

84
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:57,800
You wouldn't dare.

85
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,840
Why wouldn't I?

86
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,280
I was the one who killed her dad.

87
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:05,120
And I also killed Wang Yaqin.

88
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,280
What?

89
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,120
Why?

90
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,000
Do you still remember this?

91
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,520
You are...

92
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,320
I lost.

93
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,440
Whatever you want,
I will compensate you.

94
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,880
My dad's life,

95
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,360
how will you repay that?

96
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,720
No, no, no.

97
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,760
No.

98
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,080
You're his son.

99
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,800
This is a family heirloom.

100
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,720
He won't take it off

101
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,840
until he dies.

102
00:08:14,140 --> 00:08:15,740
I'm going to find out who really did it.

103
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,160
You are the prime suspect.

104
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,720
That's why I got close to you
on purpose

105
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,440
to gather evidence.

106
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,640
But I never expected

107
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,400
that you risked your life to save me

108
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,700
and fought side by side with me.

109
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,080
We became the best of brothers.

110
00:08:36,680 --> 00:08:37,560
All these years,

111
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,780
I tried countless times
to convince myself

112
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,840
to let go of the hatred.

113
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,440
Since you already know,

114
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:54,720
what are you going to do?

115
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,800
What am I going to do?

116
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,320
After all these years
working side by side,

117
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,360
having each other's backs,

118
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,960
you know how much I've done,

119
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,160
how many times I took the fall.

120
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,580
I've already let go of my hatred.

121
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,480
But what about them?

122
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,480
Wang Yaqin.

123
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,680
And her.

124
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:13,290
They betrayed you again and again.

125
00:09:13,290 --> 00:09:14,100
They wanted you gone.

126
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:14,920
Chu Muzhi,

127
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,240
you have no right to blame anyone.

128
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,360
You've harmed so many...

129
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,200
Shut up!

130
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,720
Chu Muzhi!

131
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,290
If you pull that trigger,
I'll end you right now.

132
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:34,720
Gu Yixiao,

133
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,560
I pretended to work with her,

134
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,880
just to show you her true colors.

135
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,920
You couldn't do it, so I did it for you.

136
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,600
I told you,

137
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:52,680
let her go first.

138
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,720
Gu Yixiao,

139
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:58,880
she's been using you from the start.

140
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,640
She never loved you.

141
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,280
But you

142
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,800
want to kill me because of her?

143
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:09,960
And you?

144
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,880
You kept saying you treat me
like a brother.

145
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,280
But from the moment
you came close to me,

146
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,800
weren't you wishing I was gone too?

147
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,040
Yeah.

148
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,840
That's exactly what I thought.

149
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,440
You're the most pitiful person alive.

150
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,800
No one cares about you.

151
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,640
Shut up.

152
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,600
Your brothers, your family,

153
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,280
even the one you love turned
against you.

154
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,600
You've got nothing left.

155
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,600
And now I'm going to take her out.

156
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,120
Muzhi...

157
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,320
Do you know

158
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:48,200
why I never went looking for evidence?

159
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,840
Because I was scared.

160
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,840
I was scared it would really be you.

161
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,120
I was scared my father's killer

162
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,760
might be my closest brother.

163
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,840
If it weren't for her,

164
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,000
we would have been

165
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,160
brothers for life.

166
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,520
This life...

167
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,040
I'm giving it back to you.

168
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,280
Buddy,

169
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:38,640
I promised you.

170
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,400
We'd rise to become

171
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,800
the strongest predators,

172
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:43,740
and no longer be trampled upon.

173
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,040
Muzhi...

174
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,920
Muzhi...

175
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,360
Muzhi...

176
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:09,720
Muzhi...

177
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:56,150
♪The fragility stripped away by you♪

178
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:59,630
♪Keeps dragging me down endlessly♪

179
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:03,950
♪If not once devoured by blazing flames♪

180
00:14:03,950 --> 00:14:07,030
♪Who would ever understand
this baptism by fire♪

181
00:14:07,310 --> 00:14:10,230
♪You betrayed me so decisively♪

182
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:13,670
♪With indifference laid bare♪

183
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:17,270
♪It taught me to stay silent first♪

184
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:20,750
♪So the explosion would be deafening♪

185
00:14:22,070 --> 00:14:27,830
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

186
00:14:29,150 --> 00:14:30,950
♪The stubborn pain♪

187
00:14:30,950 --> 00:14:37,630
♪Hardens into the hottest flame♪

188
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:44,310
♪Taste the fruit you planted,
don't ask me for mercy♪

189
00:14:44,310 --> 00:14:47,750
♪Just enjoy this searing pain♪

190
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:51,110
♪See whether blood or tears flow first♪

191
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:53,990
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

192
00:14:53,990 --> 00:14:58,430
♪Greed caused the chaos,
none can run away♪

193
00:14:58,430 --> 00:15:01,990
♪The karma you sowed by your own hands♪

194
00:15:01,990 --> 00:15:05,070
♪Watered to maturity
with blood and tears♪

195
00:15:05,310 --> 00:15:08,030
♪Then ignite the anger forged by hatred♪

196
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:12,230
♪I'll burn it all down♪
